snippet.title: Glitch Busters: Stuck on You - Exclusive Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
See the brand new gameplay trailer for Glitch Busters: Stuck on You. Join up with up to three friends to exterminate wildly weird glitches in Glitch Busters: Stuck on You. This just recently announced upcoming indie game is coming in Winter 2022 to the Nintendo Switch, PC (Steam), PS4, and PS5.

#IGN #IGNSummerofGaming
